title: Parliament House coffee shop Aussies now the centre of the gossip universe
text:
Gossip HQ. Share on twitter Share on Google Plus by Will Glasgow Rear Window has temporarily relocated from the real world to the Australian Parliament House coffee shop, Aussies â€“ which has become the centre of the gossip universe as Malcolm Turnbull , Tony Nutt and the gang work out the new Prime Minister's first ministry.
Interestingly, it also seems to be functioning as a sort of refugee camp for the frazzled staff of Tony Abbott 's decapitated Prime Minister's Office. May fortune smile on all of them. It's a brutal profession.
Federal Liberal Brian Loughnane appears to have taken on something of a pastoral role with them. Good man.
More from him in a bit.
